{"title":"拯救水滴","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":125,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-2889","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>小明正在玩一款《拯救水滴》的游戏。</p>\n<p>游戏中有5*N的沙滩，上面有一些水滴，快要蒸发了。</p>\n<p>你有一杯水，可以向任意一格滴，滴水可以连接不同片的水。</p>\n<p>如果所有水滴都连成一片，水滴就可以流走，就活了。</p>\n<p>救活它们用的水滴数就是游戏的得分。当然，得分越少越好。</p>\n<p>求小明可得的最少得分。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>第一行，整数N。</p>\n<p>之后N行01串，每行0表示无水，1表示有水。</p>\n<p> </p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>最少得分。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>4</p>\n<p>10101</p>\n<p>11011</p>\n<p>00110</p>\n<p>10000</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>2</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>N&lt;=100..</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}